   <h4>Bloom Sandbox</h4>
   


<slide class="row-fluid">
  <div class="col-sm-12">
    <h3>Using Bloom</h3>
    <br/>
    <div>
      <div class="paragraph">
<p>This Sandbox has an artificially generated dataset for exploring fraud in financial transactions.  Unlike other sandboxes, it is intended to explore in <a href="https://neo4j.com/bloom/" target="_blank">Neo4j Bloom</a>.  You should see a link for Bloom in the main Sandbox page. You can view <a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL9Hl4pk2FsvWqH11v_WXVNIgb4iHjqHgs" target="_blank">videos</a> about Bloom or read the <a href="https://neo4j.com/docs/bloom-user-guide/current/" target="_blank">User's Guide</a></p>
</div>
